title: The Raiders Should Cut Antonio Brown
itunes:title: The Raiders Should Cut Antonio Brown
description:
Colin responds to the Oakland Raiders possibly getting ready to suspended Antonio Brown, Brett Farve recent comments on the Packers offense, and what he sees wrong in Kyler Murray. Guests include Greg Jennings, Greg Cosell, T. J. Houshmandzadeh, and Brady Poppinga.
